These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
City: berlin, liverpool
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, filmmaking
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| City   | liverpool  | berlin |
| Hobby       | skydiving | filmmaking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, indian
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, roller
1. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the indian##3
2. the indian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Nationality   | australian | indian |
| Transport      | roller     | scooter  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
2 different pets are kept: mouse, bird
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, social-worker
1. the fisherman is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
2. the fisherman is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Pet   | mouse | bird  |
| Job   | fisherman | social-worker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, handball
City: hamburg, edinburgh
1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| Sport   | handball | cricket   |
| City       | edinburgh | hamburg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-5::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, july
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, chaman
1. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Birthday   | july    | april    |
| Cigar   | dannemann | chaman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-6::.
