.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-8::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk
There 2 different types of food: watermelon, kale
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | soy-milk |
| Food     | watermelon        | kale |

