.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-9::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: rock, jazz
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, comedy
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | rock  |
| Movie-Genre       | comedy   | martial-arts |

 #################################

 
